{"id": "repo_feishu_log_checks-002-knowledge_qa", "task": "knowledge_qa", "source_title": "OpenClaw Feishu Log Checks", "source_url": "repo://docs/openclaw-feishu-log-checks.md", "license": "Apache-2.0", "instruction": "请严格依据给定材料，输出结论与依据，不要添加材料之外的信息。", "input": "主题：OpenClaw Feishu Log Checks\n\n材料：\ncompute”\n按同一个 `request_id` 对齐三条日志：\n1. `API server received raw request`\n- 看到 `round1-token` 和 `round2-token`\n2. `API server received prompt`\n- 只能看到 `round2-token`\n3. `Compute server received prompt`\n- 与 API prompt 完全相同，也只能看到 `round2-token`\n只要 `API prompt` 或 `compute prompt` 里还能看到 `round1-token`，就判定失败。", "output": "结论：compute”\n按同一个 `request_id` 对齐三条日志：\n1. `API server received raw request`\n- 看到 `round1-token` 和 `round2-token`\n2. `API server received prompt`\n- 只能看到 `round2-token`\n3. `Compute server received prompt`\n- 与 API prompt 完全相同，也只能看到 `round2-token`\n只要 `API prompt` 或 `compute prompt` 里还能看到 `round1-token`，就判定失败。\n依据：\n1. compute”\n按同一个 `request_id` 对齐三条日志：\n1. `API server received raw request`\n- 看到 `round1-token` 和 `round2-token`\n2. `API server received prompt`\n- 只能看到 `round2-token`\n3. `Compute server received prompt`\n- 与 API prompt 完全相同，也只能看到 `round2-token`\n只要 `API prompt` 或 `compute prompt` 里还能看到 `round1-token`，就判定失败。", "grounding": ["compute”\n按同一个 `request_id` 对齐三条日志：\n1. `API server received raw request`\n- 看到 `round1-token` 和 `round2-token`\n2. `API server received prompt`\n- 只能看到 `round2-token`\n3. `Compute server received prompt`\n- 与 API prompt 完全相同，也只能看到 `round2-token`\n只要 `API prompt` 或 `compute prompt` 里还能看到 `round1-token`，就判定失败。"], "split": "train"}
